speeches.say: I may be blind, but there's no mistaking that smell. Can you take him out?
Yes, I...I suppose I can. Ugh...I don't feel too well.
It will wear off eventually. You need to focus!
Notice the grey 'ring' in the lower middle panel, around the exclamation mark. Wait until it turns blue.
Once the ring is blue, click on the enemy to target him. Your abilities will appear around him.
He doesn't look too happy.
He's enraged! You'll have to defend yourself! Get ready!
Target yourself instead of the enemy this turn, so you can use your defensive ability.
To find out more about an ability, hold your mouse over its icon for a couple of seconds.
Good job, Sonny. Keep going, and stay alert. There will be more of them ahead.
Wake up Frankie, the guests are here. Wake up! And make Daddy proud!
RAAAWWR!
This prison is one hell of a freak show...
Oh the horrors! I can't take it anymore! Please. Let me... taste your... blood water.
More hostiles! You've made a big mistake by breaking in here.
Sorry about the gate, I couldn't find the doorbell.
The prisoners are escaping! We need more men!
These guys are trying to escape!
Hey! HEY YOU! Did you just see a zombie chick run through here? Help us, and we'll help you!
Don't listen to him Andy, it's a trick...!
They're trying to play us for fools! You saw what they did to Frank!
Look, we just want to know if-
Back off, Mary Poppins!
You asked for it.
They're here for us, Johnny! I told you they'd come! I TOLD YOU!
Oh. What fine specimens! But you do not belong here! Guards, escort these gentlemen to the exit!
There's something fishy about this place. And it's not just the smell.
It has functional nostrils, too? Fascinating...
Oh the horrors! I can't take it anymore! Please. Let me... taste your... blood water.
There is no escape from MY prison! I will crush you!
Wake up Frankie, the guests are here. Wake up! And make Daddy proud!
RAAAWWR!
This prison is one hell of a freak show...
That uniform! Not these guys again...
It's like they're everywhere!
Ah, the meddlers...I'm sure I'll be rewarded handsomely for bringing back your heads, and thwarting your disturbance of our operation here!
Don't start what you can't finish, boys.
You’re not getting that tape!
Give us the tape, this is getting old.
You want it that bad, huh? Catch it if you can!
Isn't this a long row to hoe. Looks like we're hoofing it from here.
It was fun while it lasted, right? And look, a welcoming party!
Mmmgghrrr!
Hey, wait! You're not like the rest of them! Who are you? Can you talk?
We're just passing through. Move, or die.
Amazing!
Let's put down our weapons. We are not your enemies.
We were a group of people devoted to find a cure for... your condition. But things started happening…
Assassinations… Kidnappings… Someone didn't want us to continue our research.
Those of us that survived – we fled from the Utopia, and ended up hiding here.
This place isn't much better. The village is infested with some kind of cult.
They sacrifice innocent people. Will you help us?
Tell us how to find that Utopia. Then we will help you.
If you can rid us from this zealous cult – I'll take you there myself.
All in a days work!
Do you know anything about the prison?
A prison? Here?
No, but not far. They were conducting experiments there, on the prisoners.
Then the ZPCI showed up! Those guys just won't leave us alone.
The ZPCI? Are you sure? But they protect us - they're the good guys!
Somehow, I don't think so...
You are here to join our ranks? Then prove yourselves!
Lay down your arms, I... *cough* accept your request.
Your membership fees are too high. I'd rather kill you.
Heretic! My Master will have your heads!
We don't fear death!
Our master will save us from the undead!
What are the tattoos for? You all have them.
When things started to get ugly, we got them made in secret so we knew who we could trust.
They look familiar, somehow.
Sacrifice the intruders! Their blood will save us from death!
But nothing will save you from ME.
The master will be pleased! Die for us now!
You first. I insist!
It's their leader! If we can take him out, their cult is finished!
Ow, my head...hurting...I've felt this before!
Could it be...?
The Baron!
Oh, it’s you! You always give me trouble! And here I was, having SUCH a good time.
Not him again!
My loyal subjects are on their way here. This time, you're mine!
Let's break this bowl of fruit before the guards arrive!
No! Not again! I would've gotten away with it...if it weren't for you meddling kids!
Our master - is he one of them? He's a zombie too?
I don't believe it! All those things he said...*sobbing*
It's true, Carl, it's true!...He lied to us.
We have no reason to fight for him anymore. Let us leave this place.
Make sure no one leaves this place. Alive or dead. Disintegrate everything.
We'll take care of it Capt'n!
Quickly, come with me! We need to get underground, we can get out of here by train.
Get them! We can't leave anyone alive! DO IT!
This train is old, we'll need more fuel to get out of their range! There should be more coal in the back of the train. Let's hurry!
That's about as far as you'll go, troublemakers. The Captain wants you dead.
Spare some change?
Ow! That...hurt.
Wait a sec...that wasn't a zombie!
Well I couldn't just give him my hard earned cash, now could I?
Tickets, please!
We don't have any.
No tickets, no ride! Get off my train! GET OFF!
I can see right through you!
Just our luck. Why does everything break around us?
At least we got those ZPCI off our backs. They don't seem to be following us anymore.
These tunnels should lead us to Hew. We need to head through it if we're to reach Utopia!
The air in here... it feels different.
That one looks just like Sonny! Haha!
Hey, it kinda does!
I’m not amused.
You are my sunshine, my only sunshine...
Stop that.
I'm freaking out... man...
Oi, Miller, look! There are still people down here!
Ey, I'd give these guys some masks, if they breathe in any more of this stuff they're done for!
Put down your weapons! Resistance will be met by force.
I don't usually resort to violence, but I've got a major headache right now.
Wow, those workers are really going for it. And they're all headed to the mayor's office!
A bit more attention than I would have liked, but at least we're moving forward.
Biker girl is here too.
Quick. Cover your face.
What can we do? They're getting closer. They're going to hang me for this!
Not to worry Mayor. Plans are in motion to subdue the masses once again.
Hello boys, did you miss me?
Felicity! No! I thought you were dead! Don't let her come near me!
We're outnumbered! Where are those ZPCI when you need them?!
That ambassador was talking about a plan. What are they planning?
I won't let you kill me, you filthy corpse! I'm the Mayor!
Get out! Get out or my guards will make you! GUARDS!
Who are you? How did you find this place?
Where is the ambassador?
Ambassador? I don't know what you're talking about...
Do you know anything about a secret weapon?
You've come to the wrong place. There's nothing for you here.
Really? So what's with the high level security?
We're hunting down a target. You better leave before somebody gets hurt.
If you kill me, we won't be able to apprehend the target...
My team will have no choice but to bomb the entire region. Everything will burn, including you!
It's a bomb! Quick, dismantle it before it explodes!
This must be the target that Warden was talking about.
What IS that thing?
Criminals everywhere... This world is truly rotten.
Lady, you should be happy we killed your target for you.
Alas, only I may judge the enemy! Turn yourselves in.
Hey! That suit would look really good on Veradux. Mind if we take it?
Let them kill me, Dave! Let them kill me, and we will win.
Intruders! Stay still, let me find your melting point...
Those orbs...
